y6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_t" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_u" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Explicación:<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong> Imagina una estantería llena de <strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_v" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">cajas genéricas marrones<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong>. Tú sabes que dentro hay cosas y que todas las cajas de esa estantería tienen la misma estructura (un hueco para el nombre, otro para el precio). Pero para Spark, el contenido de cada caja es solo un objeto genérico llamado <code dir="ltr" class="KDcb0c" jsaction="" jscontroller="hNviFe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_w" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style="">Row<!--TgQPHd|[]--></code> (Fila). Spark no sabe qué hay dentro hasta que abres la caja.<!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><span jsuid="GiRUMd_x" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_x|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_y,GiRUMd_z" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_x/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_x/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_x/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_z" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="524d5521-1568-4014-be0e-f814c840a0d6" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_x|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_x|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_x|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_x/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_x/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_x/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgEEAE" data-hveid="CAEIBBAB"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;524d5521-1568-4014-be0e-f814c840a0d6&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><!--TgQPHd|[]--></ul><div class="Fsg96" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_10|npT2md" jscontroller="KHhJQ" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_10" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><div class="otQkpb" aria-level="3" role="heading" data-animation-nesting="" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="a7qCn" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_11" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true" data-sae="" style="">2. ¿Qué ventaja tiene acceder a cliente.edad frente a escribir $"edad"?<span jsuid="GiRUMd_12" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_12|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_13,GiRUMd_14" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_12/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_12/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_12/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_14" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="67791875-deb6-4f3d-9a83-a3dff6894e3d" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_12|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_12|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_12|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_12/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_12/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_12/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgFEAA" data-hveid="CAEIBRAA"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;67791875-deb6-4f3d-9a83-a3dff6894e3d&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><ul class="KsbFXc U6u95" jsaction="" jscontroller="mPWODf" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_15" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_16" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIBhAA" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_17" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_18" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Explicación:<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong><!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><ul class="KsbFXc U6u95" jsaction="" jscontroller="mPWODf" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_19" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1a" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIBhAB" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1b" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Escribir <code dir="ltr" class="KDcb0c" jsaction="" jscontroller="hNviFe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1c" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style="">$"edad"<!--TgQPHd|[]--></code> es como pedirle a un empleado: <em class="eujQNb" jsaction="" jscontroller="yHWXO" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1d" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">"Tráeme lo que haya en el cajón que dice 'edad'"<!--TgQPHd|[]--></em>. Si te equivocas y escribes <code dir="ltr" class="KDcb0c" jsaction="" jscontroller="hNviFe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1e" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style="">$"edat"<!--TgQPHd|[]--></code>, el empleado buscará por toda la fábrica y, tras perder mucho tiempo, te dirá que no existe.<!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1f" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIBhAC" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1g" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Escribir <code dir="ltr" class="KDcb0c" jsaction="" jscontroller="hNviFe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1h" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style="">cliente.edad<!--TgQPHd|[]--></code> es como tener un <strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1i" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">manual de instrucciones estricto<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong>. Si intentas escribir <code dir="ltr" class="KDcb0c" jsaction="" jscontroller="hNviFe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1j" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style="">cliente.edat<!--TgQPHd|[]--></code>, el sistema te dará un manotazo antes de empezar a trabajar y te dirá: <em class="eujQNb" jsaction="" jscontroller="yHWXO" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1k" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">"¡Ey! En el manual no existe 'edat', corrígelo antes de que echemos a andar la máquina"<!--TgQPHd|[]--></em>.<!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><span jsuid="GiRUMd_1l" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_1l|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_1m,GiRUMd_1n" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_1l/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_1l/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_1l/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_1n" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="5acc3079-17f3-44a2-9ecb-84a68b0e9bd0" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_1l|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_1l|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_1l|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_1l/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_1l/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_1l/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgGEAM" data-hveid="CAEIBhAD"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;5acc3079-17f3-44a2-9ecb-84a68b0e9bd0&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><!--TgQPHd|[]--></ul><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><!--TgQPHd|[]--></ul><div class="Fsg96" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_1o|npT2md" jscontroller="KHhJQ" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1o" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><div class="otQkpb" aria-level="3" role="heading" data-animation-nesting="" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="a7qCn" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1p" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true" data-sae="" style="">3. ¿Por qué necesitamos import spark.implicits._?<span jsuid="GiRUMd_1q" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_1q|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_1r,GiRUMd_1s" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_1q/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_1q/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_1q/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_1s" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="76a66d51-d23c-4778-b280-ad9d5fe6a0e2" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_1q|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_1q|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_1q|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_1q/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_1q/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_1q/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgHEAA" data-hveid="CAEIBxAA"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;76a66d51-d23c-4778-b280-ad9d5fe6a0e2&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><ul class="KsbFXc U6u95" jsaction="" jscontroller="mPWODf" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1t" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1u" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEICBAA" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1v" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1w" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Explicación:<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong> Es como contratar a un <strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1x" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">traductor universal<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong> para tu fábrica. Scala habla un idioma y Spark otro. Este <code dir="ltr" class="KDcb0c" jsaction="" jscontroller="hNviFe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1y" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style="">import<!--TgQPHd|[]--></code> le enseña a Spark trucos automáticos, como entender que el símbolo <code dir="ltr" class="KDcb0c" jsaction="" jscontroller="hNviFe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_1z" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style="">$<!--TgQPHd|[]--></code> significa "esto es una columna", o cómo transformar una lista normal de Scala en una tabla de Spark sin que tú tengas que programar la traducción paso a paso.<!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><span jsuid="GiRUMd_20" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_20|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_21,GiRUMd_22" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_20/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_20/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_20/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_22" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="9a2273f2-630b-41ff-905c-feb31389a64b" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_20|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_20|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_20|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_20/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_20/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_20/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgIEAE" data-hveid="CAEICBAB"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;9a2273f2-630b-41ff-905c-feb31389a64b&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><!--TgQPHd|[]--></ul><div class="Fsg96" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_23|npT2md" jscontroller="KHhJQ" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_23" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><div class="otQkpb" aria-level="3" role="heading" data-animation-nesting="" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="a7qCn" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_24" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true" data-sae="" style="">4. ¿Qué hace un Encoder?<span jsuid="GiRUMd_25" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_25|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_26,GiRUMd_27" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_25/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_25/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_25/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_27" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="17e8b0aa-4c45-4b7f-b5c0-8bdf0c8a09c7" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_25|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_25|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_25|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_25/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_25/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_25/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgJEAA" data-hveid="CAEICRAA"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;17e8b0aa-4c45-4b7f-b5c0-8bdf0c8a09c7&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><ul class="KsbFXc U6u95" jsaction="" jscontroller="mPWODf" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_28" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_29" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIChAA" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2a" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2b" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Explicación:<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong> Es el <strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2c" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">experto en embalaje<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong> de la fábrica. Si tú tienes un objeto de Scala muy complejo, el Encoder lo desarma y lo empaqueta al vacío en un formato binario supercomprimido (llamado <em class="eujQNb" jsaction="" jscontroller="yHWXO" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2d" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Tungsten<!--TgQPHd|[]--></em>). Esto hace que los datos ocupen muchísima menos memoria RAM y que Spark pueda moverlos entre servidores a toda velocidad sin tener que desenvolverlos cada vez.<!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><span jsuid="GiRUMd_2e" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_2e|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_2f,GiRUMd_2g" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_2e/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_2e/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_2e/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_2g" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="78611428-077a-4e17-965b-f8feda5f75a7" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_2e|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_2e|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_2e|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_2e/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_2e/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_2e/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgKEAE" data-hveid="CAEIChAB"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;78611428-077a-4e17-965b-f8feda5f75a7&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><!--TgQPHd|[]--></ul><div class="Fsg96" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_2h|npT2md" jscontroller="KHhJQ" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2h" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><div class="otQkpb" aria-level="3" role="heading" data-animation-nesting="" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="a7qCn" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2i" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true" data-sae="" style="">5. ¿Cuándo usarías Dataset en lugar de DataFrame?<span jsuid="GiRUMd_2j" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_2j|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_2k,GiRUMd_2l" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_2j/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_2j/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_2j/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_2l" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="9b9fe549-01c4-4422-b6c7-fe7f8a6aaf13" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_2j|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_2j|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_2j|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_2j/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_2j/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_2j/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgLEAA" data-hveid="CAEICxAA"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;9b9fe549-01c4-4422-b6c7-fe7f8a6aaf13&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><ul class="KsbFXc U6u95" jsaction="" jscontroller="mPWODf" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2m" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2n" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIDBAA" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2o" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2p" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Explicación:<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong><!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><ul class="KsbFXc U6u95" jsaction="" jscontroller="mPWODf" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2q" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2r" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIDBAB" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2s" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Usa <strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2t" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">DataFrame<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong> cuando solo quieras hacer cosas típicas de tablas: sumas, filtros, cruces de datos o sacar promedios. Es el "modo automático" y Spark vuela haciéndolo.<!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2u" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIDBAC" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2v" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Usa <strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_2w" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Dataset<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong> cuando necesites hacer "cirugía" con los datos. Por ejemplo, si tienes que aplicar una fórmula matemática hipercompleja que creaste tú mismo o usar lógica que requiera tratar cada fila como un objeto real de programación.<!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><span jsuid="GiRUMd_2x" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_2x|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_2y,GiRUMd_2z" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_2x/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_2x/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_2x/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_2z" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="cd30c535-677f-4f19-8925-5d03e2459b9b" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_2x|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_2x|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_2x|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_2x/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_2x/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_2x/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgMEAM" data-hveid="CAEIDBAD"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;cd30c535-677f-4f19-8925-5d03e2459b9b&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><!--TgQPHd|[]--></ul><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><!--TgQPHd|[]--></ul><div class="Fsg96" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_30|npT2md" jscontroller="KHhJQ" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_30" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><div class="otQkpb" aria-level="3" role="heading" data-animation-nesting="" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="a7qCn" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_31" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true" data-sae="" style="">6. ¿Por qué un error en Dataset puede aparecer antes que uno en DataFrame?<span jsuid="GiRUMd_32" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_32|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_33,GiRUMd_34" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_32/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_32/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_32/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_34" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="9503a2e5-44d5-4515-b3bf-632b8738276a" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_32|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_32|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_32|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_32/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_32/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_32/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgNEAA" data-hveid="CAEIDRAA"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></button></span><!--TgQPHd|[[null,null,&quot;9503a2e5-44d5-4515-b3bf-632b8738276a&quot;,null,null,0,0,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,0,null,null,0]]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></div><ul class="KsbFXc U6u95" jsaction="" jscontroller="mPWODf" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_35" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-processed="true"><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_36" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIDhAA" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_37" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_38" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Explicación:<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong><!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><ul class="KsbFXc U6u95" jsaction="" jscontroller="mPWODf" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_39" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_3a" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIDhAB" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_3b" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">En un <strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_3c" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">Dataset<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong>, como hay un manual estricto (la <code dir="ltr" class="KDcb0c" jsaction="" jscontroller="hNviFe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_3d" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style="">case class<!--TgQPHd|[]--></code>), el compilador lee tu código antes de arrancar y te avisa de los fallos de ortografía o de lógica matemática al instante.<!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><!--TgQPHd|[]--></li><li class="Z1qcYe" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="oSLmPe" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_3e" data-sfc-cb="" data-hveid="CAEIDhAC" data-complete="true" data-sae="" style=""><span class="T286Pc" data-sfc-cp="" jsaction="" jscontroller="fly6D" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_3f" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">En un <strong class="Yjhzub" jsaction="" jscontroller="zYmgkd" data-sfc-root="c" jsuid="GiRUMd_3g" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true">DataFrame<!--TgQPHd|[]--></strong>, Spark es más "confiado". No mira si las columnas existen de verdad hasta que el flujo de datos llega a ese punto exacto. Por eso, el programa puede estar corriendo 2 horas y fallar justo al final porque escribiste mal el nombre de una columna.<!--TgQPHd|[]--></span><span jsuid="GiRUMd_3h" class="txxDge notranslate" jsaction="rcuQ6b:&amp;GiRUMd_3h|npT2md" jscontroller="udAs2b" data-sfc-root="c" data-wiz-uids="GiRUMd_3i,GiRUMd_3j" data-sfc-cb="" data-complete="true"><span class="vKEkVd" data-animation-atomic="" data-wiz-attrbind="class=GiRUMd_3h/TKHnVd" data-sae="" style=""><span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</span><!--qkimaf GiRUMd_3h/HugV6--><!--cqw1tb GiRUMd_3h/HugV6--><button jsuid="GiRUMd_3j" tabindex="0" disabled="true" data-amic="true" data-icl-uuid="17e97bf5-3d08-4b41-b2ae-7b1229e2160c" aria-label="Ver enlaces relacionados" class="rBl3me" jsaction="click:&amp;GiRUMd_3h|S9kKve;mouseenter:&amp;GiRUMd_3h|sbHm2b;mouseleave:&amp;GiRUMd_3h|Tx5Rb" data-wiz-attrbind="disabled=GiRUMd_3h/C5gNJc;aria-label=GiRUMd_3h/bOjMyf;class=GiRUMd_3h/UpSNec" data-ved="2ahUKEwjEhtbaup-UAxXCaqQEHXAvB-EQye0OegYIAQgOEAM" data-hveid="CAEIDhAD"><span class="wiMplc ofC0Ud"><svg style="margin-top: 3px;" fill="currentColor" width="12px" height="12px" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d=